					+createDonateButton("ELG8Y2GLSXAVA", 20, 'Buy me a new book for my collection', 'Buy me a new book')
	
				.row
					| <br>You can also gift me one of the immensely interesting programming books on my 
					| <a target="_blank" href="http://www.amazon.com/wishlist/1RFQ21NSF4PAI/ref=cm_wl_prev_ret?_encoding=UTF8&reveal=">Amazon Wishlist</a>.



